sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Plugin as Federated Plugin<br/>(e.g., model-registry-ui)<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as thanos-querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access (RHOAI 3.x)

    Browser->>Gateway: HTTPS GET /dashboard<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>RBAC: HTTPS 8443/TCP<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>Gateway-forwarded headers
    RBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Can user list projects?
    K8sAPI-->>RBAC: Allowed
    RBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>plaintext (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token<br/>+ User impersonation
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: K8s Resources (CRDs, Notebooks, etc.)
    Dashboard-->>RBAC: HTML/JSON Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 2: Module Federation Plugin Access

    Browser->>Gateway: HTTPS GET /model-registry/api/*
    Gateway->>RBAC: HTTPS 8443/TCP
    RBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>X-Auth-Request-User
    Dashboard->>Plugin: HTTPS 8043/TCP<br/>TLS (shared serving cert)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Plugin->>K8sAPI: HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>User token
    K8sAPI-->>Plugin: Model Registry data
    Plugin-->>Dashboard: JSON Response
    Dashboard-->>RBAC: Proxied Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Plugin UI/Data

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>Gateway: HTTPS POST /api/prometheus
    Gateway->>RBAC: HTTPS 8443/TCP
    RBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP 8080/TCP
    Dashboard->>Thanos: HTTPS 9092/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer token (user)
    Thanos-->>Dashboard: Metrics Data
    Dashboard-->>RBAC: JSON Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Metrics JSON
